window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Rule, Adventure, Claim!</p> <p>Following the attack on Lustburg by the Wings of Freedom, Sol find himself working as a king while still being a prince.</p> <p>The Trials imposed by the goddesses await, and soon, he'll have to leave the Mortal realm to enter the Astral Realm.</p> <p>His first destination? The Phoenix Territory to conquer and sign a contract with their princess.</p>"; 
